  SCIENCE FACTS
============================================================

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Boyle's Law
Formula: P₁V₁ = P₂V₂
Note:    Pressure and volume inversely proportional at constant T

Domain:  Geology
Topic:   Plate Tectonics
Formula: ~15 major plates on mantle
Note:    Explains earthquakes, volcanoes, mountain formation

Domain:  Astronomy
Topic:   Schwarzschild Radius
Formula: r_s = 2GM/c²
Note:    Event horizon radius of a black hole

Domain:  Physics
Topic:   Wave Equation
Formula: v = fλ
Note:    Speed of wave = frequency × wavelength

Domain:  Biology
Topic:   DNA Structure
Formula: Double helix; A-T and G-C base pairs
Note:    Stores and transmits genetic information

